savvie / savvy
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:sauvignon blanc wine
Origin:abbreviation
Register: informal

Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also sav, sav blanc
Pronunciation:
Notes: Jim Cameron writes: DMNZ Slang (Orsman) is I think mistaken in calling this word an abbreviation of cabernet sauvignon. (Cf. cab sav q.v.)
